title.rendered: EEN Professionally Advisory Services – Success Story!

content.rendered:
We are thrilled to share the incredible journey of Pro Real Estate, one of the distinguished beneficiaries of the EENergy Project.With the unwavering support of the Enterprise Europe Network Kosovo, Pro Real Estate has reached new heights and our team has been there every step of the way, ensuring Pro Real Estate’s success.

Key Milestones:
 

Contract Signed

Pro Real Estate has officially signed the contract with EENergy..

Expert Guidance:

Personalized mentoring and support from EEN Kosovo advisors.

Application Submitted

Pro Real Estate has also applied to the SUSTAIN Open Call for Innovation Services and is now eagerly awaiting the results.

Funding Opportunities

Access to various SMP funding opportunities through EEN Kosovo.

International B2B Events

Participation in international B2B events to expand their network and business reach.

Check out the full video to see the remarkable transformation and hear directly from the team at Pro Real Estate about their experience and achievements!
 
Watch the video now and get inspired by their success story!
